sentences.sContent: I want to make it clear, however, that no one is untouchable in this investigation.
sentences.sCn: 但是，我想说清楚，没有人可以免于接受这次调查。

synos.tran: 达不到的；不可批评的；不可捉摸的

trans.tranCn: 达不到的；不可批评的；不可捉摸的
trans.tranOther: If you say that someone is untouchable, you mean that they cannot be affected or punished in any way
